reviewText: Well, then I drected it so...

I've seen the whole series on TV and noticed it is based on the org. series of ABC KANE by filmer Hugo van Lawick. It's a pitty it's decided to spare on tape cost,
these are poor copies on Extended Play format delivering blurred soft focus, this in contrast to the tv-transmissions and my original tapes. Remastered sound gets a 4*!
